<h2>Recipe: {{model.recipe.beer.name}} {{if hasUnsavedChanges "*" ""}}</h2>
<p>Creator: {{model.recipe.creator.fullName}}</p>
<p>Pre Boil Volume: {{input type="number" value=model.recipe.preBoilVolume}} l</p>
<p>Cold Pre Boil Volume: {{model.recipe.preBoilVolumeCold}} l</p>
<h3>Mashing</h3>
<p>Malt:</p>
<ul>
	{{#each model.recipe.mashEntries as |entry|}}
	<li>{{entry.ingredient.name}}: {{format-number entry.weight 2}} kg, Extract: {{format-number entry.ingredient.extractYield 3}} ({{clickable-text value=entry.amount}}%)</li>
	{{/each}}
	<li>Unassigned: {{model.recipe.unassignedMalt}}%</li>
</ul>
<p>Total Malt Weight: {{input type="number" step="0.1" value=model.recipe.totalMaltWeight}} kg</p>
<p>Water/Malt Ratio: {{format-number model.recipe.waterToMaltRatio 2}}</p>
<p>Water Absorbed By Malt: {{format-number model.recipe.absorbedByMalt 2}} l</p>
<p>Mashing Temp: {{input type="number" value=model.recipe.mashingTemp}} &deg;C</p>
<p>Mashing Time: {{input type="number" value=model.recipe.mashingTime}} min</p>
<p>Mash Out Temp: {{input type="number" value=model.recipe.mashOutTemp}} &deg;C</p>
<p>Mash Out Time: {{input type="number" value=model.recipe.mashOutTime}} min</p>
<p>Strike Water Volume: {{format-number model.recipe.strikeWaterVolume 1}} l</p>
<p>Strike Water Temp: {{format-number model.recipe.strikeWaterTemp 1}} &deg;C</p>
<p>Average Extract Yield: {{format-number model.recipe.averageExtractYieldRounded 3}}</p>
<p>Max First Wort SG: {{format-number model.recipe.maxFirstWortSG 3}}</p>
<p>Estimated First Wort SG: {{format-number model.recipe.firstWortSG 3}} (Estimated CE: 95%)</p>
<h3>Lautering</h3>
<p>Sparge Water Volume: {{model.recipe.spargeWaterVolume}} l</p>
<p>Estimated Lauter Efficiency: {{format-number model.recipe.lauterEfficiency 1}}%</p>
<p>Estimated Brewhouse Efficienct: {{format-number model.recipe.brewhouseEfficiency 1}}%</p>
<p>Pre Boil SG: {{format-number model.recipe.preBoilSG 3}}</p>
<h3>Boiling</h3>
<p>Post Boil Volume (Cold): {{format-number model.recipe.postBoilVolumeCold 1}}</p>
<p>OG: {{format-number model.recipe.OG 3}}</p>
<h3>Fermentation</h3>
<p>Yeast: {{#power-select options=model.yeasts selected=model.recipe.yeast onchange=(action (mut model.recipe.yeast)) as |yeast|}}
	{{yeast.name}}
{{/power-select}}</p>
<button {{action "saveModel"}}>Save</button>